    public static interface Client.LogMessageHandler

      void onLogMessage(int verbosityLevel, java.lang.String message)

    • Method Detail

      • onLogMessage

        void onLogMessage(int verbosityLevel,
                  java.lang.String message)
        Callback called on messages that are added to the internal TDLib log.
        Parameters:
        verbosityLevel - Log verbosity level with which the message was added from -1 up to 1024. If 0, then TDLib will crash as soon as the callback returns. None of the TDLib methods can be called from the callback.
        message - The message added to the internal TDLib log.
